f, here are some ideas on what to put in a gift basket to make it special.","<strong>Step One: Select a Theme</strong><br/>Having a theme helps you decide what items to put in your basket and gives it a quality of completion. Occasions make obvious themes, and you&#39;ll find most gift basket stores have baskets around birthdays, weddings, holidays and the like. But for a unique gift basket, choose a theme around your recipient&#39;s interest: a hobby or favorite movie genre, or a dream or ambition, like traveling to Europe or writing a novel."]},"id":"f0a033e3-e7a3-4f40-aa31-70fc22a72b1f","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/G7PdZTWaqg7EVspgEoqkmR.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Pick a few items centered on that theme. Try to find some of different sizes. Most baskets focus on foods, but when making your own, you can put anything in: toys, calendars, tools, books or knickknacks. Don&#39;t feel like you have to spend a lot of money, either. Sometimes the most interesting things can be found in thrift shops or secondhand stores. It&#39;s a good method for regifting as well.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/8476/gift-basket-ide-7.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/G7PdZTWaqg7EVspgEoqkmR.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"G7PdZTWaqg7EVspgEoqkmR","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/G7PdZTWaqg7EVspgEoqkmR.jpg","alt":""},"id":"ffc4edfe-da62-4c33-bfb0-8fef7b0dd812","type":"image"},{"data":{"path":"/L2fCKeEJTCYXRtKS7tgTgY.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"In this example, I started with &#34;Star Wars&#34; as the theme. The toys and calendars are found in retail stores, but the Chewbacca cup came from a thrift shop. Isn&#39;t he darling, though?","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/misc/articles/8476/gift-basket-ide-8.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/L2fCKeEJTCYXRtKS7tgTgY.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"L2fCKeEJTCYXRtKS7t